{
  "stem": "23626.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There were some people that were with him in cattle car.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think, from what my friends told me who escaped-- and they ask my father to follow, to come with him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I think my father-- and it's unbelievable, because my father was always such a happy individual and-- but at that point, from what my friends are telling me, he must have given up, because he sat very quietly and refused to jump.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But thinking about it back, my dad had a condition.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He-- he was supposed to be operated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He had a hernia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when the SS men came in and grabbed him, he didn't even take his truss that he was wearing to support his condition, hernia condition.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So it's dreadful [SIGHS] for me to tell you this, but thinking about this, how he must have suffered those few days with this condition, that probably that's why he didn't jump out the window.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But those two people did jump out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they told me that my father was sitting, like, giving up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, he was a very smart man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "At that point, he already must have known that it's not very good anymore.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It wasn't the same man that I remembered, from what my friends told me how he sat-- was sitting there and didn't even try to jump, while those two friends of mine did jump out the-- through the window, from the running train.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] I did meet a gentleman in our society, Krakow society, that always was telling me and my sister how my dear father was always trying to help him financially.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He-- he had nine children.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
